To make and then install the library, execute the following
commands respectively into the project directory.

- make
- make install

make builds the library, so no need any root permission.
However, to install the library, you need root permission.
if the /usr/local/lib directory is not set your
LD_LIBRARY_PATH variable, please execute the following
command before writing any application including the library
or executing example project into the example directory.

- export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/usr/local/lib/
